{"tid":2287931,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警察\"銀行\" : 警察儲蓄互助社 (2)","createTime":"2020-11-16T06:37:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-18T07:46:32.000Z","uid":197256,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0efef630013a37f8a663a183ba9c72b44842fe7e","tid":2287931,"uid":197256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T06:37:47.000Z","msg":"呢間野係咪洗緊黑錢？<br />\n<br />\n警察儲蓄互助社<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkpcu.org/ct/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkpcu.org%2Fct%2F&d=fL1pPRntFf1zvvLBqslw3pnDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=6dbfd53b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkpcu.org/ct/</a><br />\n警察係有佢哋自己既&quot;銀行&quot; . 呢間嘢係存款超高息, 借錢超低息(有D 係冇息)<br />\n買樓, 屋企人讀書. 都可以問呢間嘢用超低息嚟借. <br />\n仲有. 之前黑警被打爛D 車呀. 窗呀. 醫療費呀....都可以去呢間嘢CLAIM 返錢<br />\n呢間嘢資產聽聞係有成千億. 實力雄厚<br />\n所以你哋話黑警俾人CALL LOAN. 而家應該未有可能住. 因為佢哋唔係問一般銀行借<br />\n唔好再話黑警會俾銀行追數...D 狗肯定會私下笑鳩你. <br />\nPS. 上面資料可能有出入(戴返個頭盔先)<br />\n千祈唔好起呢間嘢底, SEND 資料俾外國. 千祈唔好. 犯法的. 真係千祈唔好."},{"pid":"98f3f3c24f7d3cf065b85181e290ec9ee7a9ca27","tid":2287931,"uid":346701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T06:49:19.000Z","msg":"成日睇錯個名做 警畜互助社"},{"pid":"8dc0d41c680f57d9d9b9956cb36a2aa4068cd2ae","tid":2287931,"uid":364770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T06:50:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbb86fb5c0563bd0c20ed0d1484d30ed9164775b","tid":2287931,"uid":123848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T06:55:55.000Z","msg":"狗多數爛賭，依個爛賭會黎，<br />\n借完，一出糧就係戶口扣，無得走，<br />\n可以睇到D狗呃左市民咁多錢，<br />\n全數落晒黑幫到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69b7b5fc2aeaab089a64349dc0b0795cce0347cf","tid":2287931,"uid":197256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T07:46:32.000Z","ms